&lt;p&gt;I have committed a quick fix in Rev. 924787 (just leaving the modify() method if there is no instance). &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can you check, whether that fixes your issue ? Thanks alot.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
